data.description: Back on the market at no fault of it's own! This beautiful 3-bedroom 2 bath home on .80-acre lot with NO HOA is waiting for you! Nestled off the road, the cozy front porch overlooking the front yard is extremely private showcasing beautiful large oak trees. This mature lot has a multitude of different tree species and has been maintained pridefully. The large front yard is not to be outdone by the massive backyard with a fenced in area for your pets and an additional 2-bay detached garage/workshop insulated with electrical for all your tools, toys, or man cave desires! Inside you will find a spacious living room with a fireplace, and beautiful bamboo flooring throughout the main areas of the home. The kitchen is a dining combo with solid surface counter tops, abundant counter space. There is also a large Carolina room off the backside of the dining area for all-season enjoyment. The master bedroom has a large walk-in closet, an attached master bath with a large walk-in shower, tile floor, and double vanity! If you are looking for garage space... this home has it! The attached 2 car garage is also massive and has a convenient side door. New roof in 2021 and HVAC was all updated within the last 2 years. This home is ready to move in and be your home sweet home. Just minutes away from downtown Conway, restaurants, shopping, and multiple boat landings! Call today to book your showing!
